description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Full Body Beginner Dumbbell Workout' from the channel growwithjo.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Its time to get our sweat on, but with a STRENGTH workout this time! 
This full body dumbbell workout at home is perfect to build lean muscle and see amazing changes in your physique.

This dumbbell workout is complete with a warm up (bodyweight) and cool down to make sure that your heart rate comes up at a safe pace, and you cool down for maximum recovery. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x4MHzjnSayc&t=9s
